Special Line Rider Privacy Policy

Effective Date: 31/8/2025

1. Introduction

Special Line Delivery Services ("we," "us," or "our") values your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and protect your information when you use our Special Line Rider mobile application (the "App"). Please read this Privacy Policy carefully.

2. Information We Collect

- Personal Information: When you register an account, we collect information such as your name, email address, phone number, and delivery address.
- Usage Data: We may collect data on how the app is accessed and used, including device information, IP addresses, and other diagnostic data.
- Location Information: If you permit us, we collect and use your location data to enhance your delivery experience, including providing real-time tracking of deliveries.
- Camera Usage: We collect images and scan QR codes using the camera to facilitate order processing, delivery verification, and other app functionalities.

3. How We Use Your Information

- To Provide and Maintain Services: We use the information to deliver and maintain our services, including processing deliveries and providing customer support.
- To Improve the App: We analyze your usage to understand your preferences and enhance your experience.
- To Communicate with You: We use your contact information to send important updates, such as changes to our terms, and to respond to your inquiries.
- Camera Data Usage: Images captured and QR codes scanned through the camera are used for verifying deliveries, managing orders, and enhancing user experience.

4. Data Sharing and Disclosure

- Service Providers: We may share your information with third-party service providers who assist us in operating the App, such as payment processors, customer support services, and analytics providers.
- Legal Compliance: We may disclose your information if required to do so by law or in response to valid requests by public authorities.

5. Your Rights and Choices

- Access and Correction: You have the right to access and correct the personal data we hold about you.
- Withdrawal of Consent: You may withdraw your consent to the collection and use of your data at any time by adjusting the settings in the App or contacting us at privacy@specialline.ae.

6. Data Security

We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction.

7. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on the App or our website. Your continued use of the App after the changes will constitute your acceptance of the updated policy.

8. Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at privacy@specialline.ae.
